 185:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        *** High frequency interface mode ***
 186:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        =====================================
 187:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        [..]
 188:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        The high frequency interface informs DAC instance about the bus frequency in use.
 189:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        It is mandatory information for DAC (as internal timing of DAC is bus frequency dependent)
 190:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        provided thanks to parameter DAC_HighFrequency handled in HAL_DAC_ConfigChannel () function.
 191:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        Use of DAC_HIGH_FREQUENCY_INTERFACE_MODE_AUTOMATIC value of DAC_HighFrequency is recommended
 192:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        function figured out the correct setting.
 193:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        The high frequency mode is same for all converters of a same DAC instance. Either same
 194:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        parameter DAC_HighFrequency is used for all DAC converters or again self
 195:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****        DAC_HIGH_FREQUENCY_INTERFACE_MODE_AUTOMATIC detection parameter.
 196:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c **** 
 197:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****      [..]
 198:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****     (@) For Dual mode and specific signal (Triangle and noise) generation please
 199:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dac.c ****         refer to Extended Features Driver description
